title: Giants-Patriots TNF Preview (Football 10/10)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Tyler Sullivan to preview Thursday's matchup between the Giants and Patriots. The guys break down New York's injuries, how to protect Daniel Jones, New England's defense and if their offense is actually any good, before giving their picks and going over player props for the game.
